  "title": "Corporate Secretarial, Senior Executive / Executive",
  "description": "<p>Our Client is a corporate service provider with a growing Corporate Secretarial Practice.  In line with their expansion plans, they are looking to add to the team at the Executive / Senior Executive level.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>You will be part of a dynamic team within our corporate secretarial practice providing a full suite of corporate secretarial services to a portfolio of clients (comprising listed companies and privately-owned entities) and will also have the opportunity to be involved in transactional engagements with the associated law practice from time to time.</p><p>In addition to an attractive remuneration package, we will provide the necessary training and skills development to enhance your professional and career development.</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least <strong>2* </strong>years* of experience in <strong>corporate secretarial </strong>work</li><li>Attention to details</li><li>Willing to learn and take on challenge & positive work attitude</li><li>Good time management and ability to meet deadlines</li><li>Possess a high level of integrity, professionalism and strong sense of responsibility</li><li>Able to work independently, resourceful and self-motivated</li></ul><p>We encourage interested qualified candidates to email an updated resume in <u>word </u>doc format to <a href=\"mailto:enquiry@targetpartners.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">enquiry@targetpartners.com.sg </a>indicating current and expected compensation.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>[Joe Chua, R1105627]</p>",
